# Figma Export Mapping

This document describes how to map Figma components and their properties for export.

## Figma Mapping Structure

- `components`: List of components that are being exported.
- `properties`: Definitions of the properties for each component.

```json
{
  "components": [
    {
      "name": "ComponentName",
      "properties": {
        "property1": "value1",
        "property2": "value2"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```
